--}}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Case Risk Assessment Report</title>
  <style>
    {{{print_css}}}

    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 15mm;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 10pt;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Document Header */
    .doc-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5em;
      padding-bottom: 1em;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
    }

    .doc-header h1 {
      font-size: 16pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 0.25em 0;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .doc-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #5b21b6);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.4em 1em;
      font-size: 9pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    /* Case Details */
    .case-details {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0.5em 2em;
      background: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 1em;
      margin: 1.5em 0;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 9pt;
    }

    .case-details dt {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
    }

    .case-details dd {
      margin: 0;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    /* Risk Score */
    .risk-score-container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2em;
      margin: 1.5em 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .risk-score-container.strong {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dcfce7, #bbf7d0);
      border: 2px solid #22c55e;
    }

    .risk-score-container.moderate {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
      border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
    }

    .risk-score-container.weak {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2, #fecaca);
      border: 2px solid #dc2626;
    }

    .risk-score {
      font-size: 48pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 0.25em;
    }

    .risk-score-container.strong .risk-score { color: #15803d; }
    .risk-score-container.moderate .risk-score { color: #b45309; }
    .risk-score-container.weak .risk-score { color: #dc2626; }

    .risk-label {
      font-size: 14pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    .risk-description {
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Progress Bar */
    .progress-bar {
      height: 12px;
      background: #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 6px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 1em auto;
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .progress-bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: width 0.3s;
    }

    .progress-bar-fill.strong { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #16a34a); }
    .progress-bar-fill.moderate { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); }
    .progress-bar-fill.weak { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc2626, #b91c1c); }

    /* Section Headers */
    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75em;
      margin: 2em 0 1em 0;
      padding-bottom: 0.5em;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    }

    .section-header .num {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: white;
      width: 1.75em;
      height: 1.75em;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11pt;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 12pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    /* Lists */
    .strength-list, .warning-list, .recommendation-list {
      margin: 1em 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .strength-list li, .warning-list li, .recommendation-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75em;
      padding: 0.75em;
      margin: 0.5em 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .strength-list li {
      background: #dcfce7;
      border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
    }

    .warning-list li.red-flag {
      background: #fee2e2;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
    }

    .warning-list li.compliance {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    }

    .warning-list li.evidence {
      background: #e0e7ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
    }

    .recommendation-list li {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a;
    }

    .list-icon {
      font-size: 14pt;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .list-content {
      flex: 1;
      font-size: 9pt;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Info Boxes */
    .info-box {
      margin: 1.5em 0;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .info-box-header {
      padding: 0.75em 1em;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    .info-box-content {
      padding: 1em;
      font-size: 9pt;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .info-box-content p {
      margin: 0.5em 0;
    }

    .timeline-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: 0.25em 1em;
    }

    .timeline-grid dt {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
    }

    .timeline-grid dd {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .cost-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 9pt;
    }

    .cost-table th, .cost-table td {
      padding: 0.5em;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .cost-table th {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Disclaimer */
    .disclaimer {
      margin: 2em 0;
      padding: 1em;
      background: #f8f8f8;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: #666;
    }

    .disclaimer h3 {
      font-size: 9pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
      color: #444;
    }

    .disclaimer ol {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 1.25em;
    }

    .disclaimer li {
      margin: 0.3em 0;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .doc-footer {
      margin-top: 2em;
      padding-top: 1em;
      border-top: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: #666;
    }

    .doc-footer p {
      margin: 0.3em 0;
    }

    @media print {
      .info-box,
      .risk-score-container {
        page-break-inside: avoid;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Document Header -->
<div class="doc-header">
  <h1>Case Risk Assessment</h1>
  <span class="doc-badge">Ask Heaven AI Analysis</span>
</div>

<!-- Case Details -->
<dl class="case-details">
  <dt>Landlord:</dt>
  <dd>{{landlord_name}}</dd>
  <dt>Property:</dt>
  <dd>{{property_address}}</dd>
  <dt>Tenant:</dt>
  <dd>{{tenant_name}}</dd>
  <dt>Case Type:</dt>
  <dd>{{case_type}}</dd>
  <dt>Jurisdiction:</dt>
  <dd>England & Wales</dd>
  <dt>Assessment Date:</dt>
  <dd>{{current_date}}</dd>
</dl>

<!-- Risk Score -->
{{#if (gte risk_assessment.success_probability 70)}}
<div class="risk-score-container strong">
  <div class="risk-score">{{risk_assessment.success_probability}}%</div>
  <div class="risk-label">Strong Case</div>
  <div class="progress-bar">
    <div class="progress-bar-fill strong" style="width: {{risk_assessment.success_probability}}%"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="risk-description">High likelihood of success. Proceed with confidence, ensuring all compliance requirements are met.</div>
</div>
{{else if (gte risk_assessment.success_probability 50)}}
<div class="risk-score-container moderate">
  <div class="risk-score">{{risk_assessment.success_probability}}%</div>
  <div class="risk-label">Moderate Case</div>
  <div class="progress-bar">
    <div class="progress-bar-fill moderate" style="width: {{risk_assessment.success_probability}}%"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="risk-description">Reasonable likelihood of success. Address issues below to strengthen your position.</div>
</div>
{{else}}
<div class="risk-score-container weak">
  <div class="risk-score">{{risk_assessment.success_probability}}%</div>
  <div class="risk-label">Weak Case</div>
  <div class="progress-bar">
    <div class="progress-bar-fill weak" style="width: {{risk_assessment.success_probability}}%"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="risk-description">Significant concerns identified. Address all red flags before proceeding.</div>
</div>
{{/if}}

<!-- Case Strengths -->
<div class="section-header">
  <span class="num">1</span>
  <h2>Case Strengths</h2>
</div>

{{#if risk_assessment.strengths}}
<ul class="strength-list">
  {{#each risk_assessment.strengths}}
  <li>
    <span class="list-icon">‚úÖ</span>
    <span class="list-content">{{this}}</span>
  </li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{else}}
<p style="padding: 1em; background: #f8f8f8; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 9pt;">
  Based on the information provided, specific strengths have not been identified. Consider strengthening your case by ensuring all compliance requirements are met and gathering comprehensive evidence.
</p>
{{/if}}

<!-- Red Flags -->
<div class="section-header">
  <span class="num">2</span>
  <h2>Critical Issues</h2>
</div>

{{#if risk_assessment.red_flags}}
<ul class="warning-list">
  {{#each risk_assessment.red_flags}}
  <li class="red-flag">
    <span class="list-icon">üö®</span>
    <span class="list-content">{{this}}</span>
  </li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 1em; padding: 0.75em; background: #fee2e2; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 9pt;">
  <strong>ACTION REQUIRED:</strong> These are serious issues that could block or significantly weaken your case. Address these BEFORE proceeding.
</p>
{{else}}
<p style="padding: 1em; background: #dcfce7; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 9pt;">
  ‚úÖ <strong>No critical red flags identified.</strong> Your case does not have any major blockers.
</p>
{{/if}}

<!-- Compliance Issues -->
{{#if risk_assessment.compliance_issues}}
<div class="section-header">
  <span class="num">3</span>
  <h2>Compliance Concerns</h2>
</div>

<ul class="warning-list">
  {{#each risk_assessment.compliance_issues}}
  <li class="compliance">
    <span class="list-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
    <span class="list-content">{{this}}</span>
  </li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

<!-- Missing Evidence -->
{{#if risk_assessment.missing_evidence}}
<div class="section-header">
  <span class="num">{{#if risk_assessment.compliance_issues}}4{{else}}3{{/if}}</span>
  <h2>Missing Evidence</h2>
</div>

<ul class="warning-list">
  {{#each risk_assessment.missing_evidence}}
  <li class="evidence">
    <span class="list-icon">üìÑ</span>
    <span class="list-content">{{this}}</span>
  </li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

<!-- Recommendations -->
<div class="section-header">
  <span class="num">{{#if risk_assessment.missing_evidence}}{{#if risk_assessment.compliance_issues}}5{{else}}4{{/if}}{{else}}{{#if risk_assessment.compliance_issues}}4{{else}}3{{/if}}{{/if}}</span>
  <h2>Recommendations</h2>
</div>

{{#if risk_assessment.recommendations}}
<ol class="recommendation-list" style="list-style: decimal; padding-left: 1.5em;">
  {{#each risk_assessment.recommendations}}
  <li style="background: #f8f8f8; border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 0.75em; margin: 0.5em 0; border-radius: 4px;">
    <span class="list-content">{{this}}</span>
  </li>
  {{/each}}
</ol>
{{else}}
<ol class="recommendation-list" style="list-style: decimal; padding-left: 1.5em;">
  <li style="background: #f8f8f8; border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 0.75em; margin: 0.5em 0; border-radius: 4px;">Address all red flags and compliance issues first</li>
  <li style="background: #f8f8f8; border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 0.75em; margin: 0.5em 0; border-radius: 4px;">Gather comprehensive evidence to support your case</li>
  <li style="background: #f8f8f8; border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 0.75em; margin: 0.5em 0; border-radius: 4px;">Ensure you follow correct legal procedure</li>
  <li style="background: #f8f8f8; border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 0.75em; margin: 0.5em 0; border-radius: 4px;">Keep detailed records of all communications</li>
  <li style="background: #f8f8f8; border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 0.75em; margin: 0.5em 0; border-radius: 4px;">Seek legal advice if case is complex</li>
</ol>
{{/if}}

<!-- Timeline Estimate -->
<div class="info-box">
  <div class="info-box-header">üìÖ Estimated Timeline</div>
  <div class="info-box-content">
    <dl class="timeline-grid">
      <dt>Notice Period:</dt>
      <dd>14 days - 2 months (depending on route)</dd>
      <dt>Court Processing:</dt>
      <dd>4-8 weeks</dd>
      <dt>Hearing (if contested):</dt>
      <dd>8-16 weeks</dd>
      <dt>Possession Order:</dt>
      <dd>After hearing</dd>
      <dt>Bailiff Eviction:</dt>
      <dd>2-6 weeks after order</dd>
    </dl>
    <p style="margin-top: 1em; color: #666;"><strong>Typical Total:</strong> 4-7 months (varies based on court workload, tenant defense, and case complexity)</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Cost Estimate -->
<div class="info-box">
  <div class="info-box-header">üí∞ Cost Estimate</div>
  <div class="info-box-content">
    <table class="cost-table">
      <tr>
        <th>Item</th>
        <th>Cost</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Possession Claim Court Fee</td>
        <td>¬£325 - ¬£355</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Bailiff Warrant</td>
        <td>¬£121 - ¬£130</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Solicitor (if needed)</td>
        <td>¬£1,500 - ¬£3,000+</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <p style="margin-top: 1em; font-size: 8pt; color: #666;">Court fees may be recoverable if you win. Lost rent during proceedings is typically not recoverable.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Disclaimer -->
<div class="disclaimer">
  <h3>Important Disclaimers</h3>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Not Legal Advice:</strong> This assessment is based on general legal principles and is not a substitute for professional legal advice.</li>
    <li><strong>Courts Have Discretion:</strong> Even strong cases can face unexpected challenges. Courts consider many factors.</li>
    <li><strong>Information Accuracy:</strong> This assessment assumes all provided information is accurate and complete.</li>
    <li><strong>Success Not Guaranteed:</strong> A high score indicates likelihood, not certainty. Many factors affect outcomes.</li>
  </ol>
</div>

<!-- Footer -->
<div class="doc-footer">
  <p><strong>Generated by Ask Heaven AI:</strong> {{current_date}}</p>
  <p><strong>Landlord Heaven</strong> | Case Risk Assessment Report</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
